## ğŸ“ After You Get the Key

Once you have the key, run:

```powershell
# 1. Set the key
$env:ANTHROPIC_API_KEY = "sk-ant-your-key"

# 2. Make sure Gemini key is set
$env:GEMINI_API_KEY = "your-gemini-key"

# 3. Test both keys
python scripts/test_claude_key.py

# 4. Run the experiment
python scripts/run_llm_baseline_experiment.py --baseline claude

# 5. Generate visualizations
python scripts/visualize_llm_comparison.py reports/llm_baseline_comparison_claude_*.json
```

